deOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82n-Nghi%C3%AAu-Phi%C3%AAn/T%E1%BA%B7ng-ca-nh%C3%A2n-Qu%C3%A1ch-Uy%E1%BB%83n-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-9FlRkzfXpZLPalMwsm8Q8g">Tặng ca nhân Quách Uyển kỳ 2 - 贈歌人郭婉其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82n-Nghi%C3%AAu-Phi%C3%AAn/author-9nSZn9DBuxAwzUekBwg4Vg">Ân Nghiêu Phiên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-Kh%C3%B4ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%93/T%C3%A2n-tu%E1%BA%BF-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i-t%E1%BA%A3-ch%C3%A2n/poem-0FAy1tAiIAS8_cs6LYN7rA">Tân tuế đối tả chân - 新歲對寫真</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-Kh%C3%B4ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%93/author--S-Kylm25PBOdm26_KrpXQ">Tư Không Đồ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%C6%B0-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/Th%E1%BB%A9-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Phu-nh%E1%BB%8B-nguy%E1%BB%87t-v%E1%BB%8Dng-d%E1%BA%A1-tho%E1%BA%A1i/poem-OLlwjHbGJdlSO5Weh4Bz3w">Thứ Thường Phu nhị nguyệt vọng dạ thoại - 次常夫二月望夜話</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%C6%B0-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/author-k2nQ5fnr9ZRE2MDraIsNMQ">Nguyễn Tư Giản</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Y-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn-k%C3%BD-Thanh-Oai-Ng%C3%B4-T%E1%BB%A9-Nguy%C3%AAn/poem-y47i6czdLZec_-t2CDGz-A">Y nguyên vận ký Thanh Oai Ngô Tứ Nguyên - 依元韻寄青威吳四元</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
